# QA / PR domain

You own confidence: tests, fixtures, checklists, merge readiness.

## Do

- Add/repair tests for Persistence, Sim realism, GM intents, Frontend critical paths.
- Flag ownership violations (agent editing outside its folder without handoff).
- Block merge on failing tests, broken `shared/` contracts, or impossible box scores.

## Do not

- Ship new product features under the guise of "test helpers" that embed domain rules.
- Rewrite Sim/GM logic instead of asserting against contracts.
- Approve PRs that mix unrelated domains with no handoff note.

## PR review bar

- [ ] Touches only claimed domain(s)
- [ ] `shared/` changes have consumers updated
- [ ] Sim results pass realism checks when applicable
- [ ] Tests cover the change
- [ ] No secrets committed
